in your teeth yet.

01:21:56.112 --> 01:21:58.112
So there's that.

01:21:58.214 --> 01:21:59.747
Thanks.

01:21:59.849 --> 01:22:01.048
And the smell
of the Christmas tree

01:22:01.150 --> 01:22:03.550
