01:22:17.566 --> 01:22:20.367
Hey, Darcy, who's
the extra place setting for?

01:22:20.469 --> 01:22:22.469
Oh, just you wait.

01:22:25.007 --> 01:22:27.041
- Hey, come on in.
- Hey. Thanks.

01:22:27.143 --> 01:22:28.542
- Hey, Tom.
- Hey.

01:22:28.644 --> 01:22:30.711
